.TH kill_spider 1 "4 Jan 2000" "Local Software"
.SH NAME
kill_spider \- stop the spider daemon.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kill_spider
.SH DESCRIPTION
.LP
The command
.B kill_spider
will terminate the 
.BR spider (8)
daemon, by looking at the pid file and sending it a TERM signal.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spider (8).
